    <node id="Shifted Factorial">
      <data key="d0">Shifted Factorial</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">A mathematical construct where the 0-th value is 1 and the n-th value is defined for positive integers.&lt;SEP&gt;A mathematical definition representing the product of consecutive terms defined by the Pochhammer symbol formula.</data>
