    <node id="Modified Abel Lemma">
      <data key="d0">Modified Abel Lemma</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">A lemma on summation by parts that relies on the existence of a certain limit and convergence of series.&lt;SEP&gt;A specific version of the Abel lemma providing operational simplification for summation techniques based on q-analogues.&lt;SEP&gt;The concept represented by Mathematical Equation (3), specifically concerning summation by parts.&lt;SEP&gt;A mathematical lemma defined in the preliminaries section applied in the application of tools.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-90fca6d9f1f9b0dbe01302d6bf68c233&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-948f619adaa6af7493a36bc96cd93d44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b543e65153eeae6b53b00ef9af95c9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d128add90e7f551a5bf0aa11f3f4b9a6</data>
