    <node id="Forward Difference Operator">
      <data key="d0">Forward Difference Operator</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">An operator defined for a sequence where the value is the difference between the n-th and n-plus-1-th terms.&lt;SEP&gt;The operator defined as $\Delta \tau_n = \tau_n - \tau_{n+1}$, acting as the negative of the standard forward difference.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-90fca6d9f1f9b0dbe01302d6bf68c233&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-948f619adaa6af7493a36bc96cd93d44</data>
